description:
The Rubik's Cube takes the transformation of the game as the starting point. By establishing a scientific and reasonable game system, it promotes the Rubik's Cube simulation game to the whole world, promotes quality education and parent-child interactive education, develops the learner's brain in an all-round way, and comprehensively improves the quality of quality education.

As the world's first multi-dimensional blockchain combining "Internet of Things + Rubik's Cube + Game", the Rubik's Cube is a virtual trading currency that can be traded globally.
name: Magic Stone Fund
